heading: 2. The 21st day of February 2020 is appointed as the day on which the
text_raw:
2. The 21st day of February 2020 is appointed as the day on which the 
Coroners (Amendment) Act 2019 (No. 29 of 2019), in so far as it is not already 
in operation, shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

13 February, 2020. 

CHARLES FLANAGAN, 

Minister for Justice and Equality. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 21st February, 2020.
